                <div class="how_led_works pt-30 pt-md-60">
                    <p class="fs-24"><strong>How LED light therapy works</strong></p>
                    <p>At home LED light therapy devices have been created so you can treat skin problems at
                        home on your own. The light doesn’t cause any burns or skin damage, it is painless
                        with no down time.</p>
                    <p>LED light therapy harnesses the healing power of light for complete skin
                        rejuvenation. LED light therapy works on a cellular level to tackle a huge range of
                        skin concerns. It is really quite incredible!</p>
                </div>
                <div class="epidermis pt-30 pt-md-60">
