                </div>
                <div class="benefits_of_led pt-30 pt-md-60">
                    <p class="fs-24"><strong>What are the benefits of LED light therapy?</strong></p>
                    <p>People are turning to LED light therapy to fix skin problems such as acne. In fact,
                        it works well for a variety of skin conditions, from eczema, to rosacea, and so much
                        more.</p>
                    <p>Light therapy has an extensive list of amazing benefits such as;</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Stimulates collagen production</li>
                        <li>Smooths fine lines and wrinkles</li>
                        <li>Reduces redness and inflammation</li>
                        <li>Prevents breakouts by killing the acne-causing bacteria</li>
                        <li>Minimizes pores by regulating oil production</li>
                        <li>Improves appearance of scarring by promoting skin cell healing</li>
                        <li>Brightens skin and dark spots</li>
                        <li>Smooths skin texture</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="how_to_prepare pt-30 pt-md-60">
                    <p class="fs-24"><strong>How to Prepare for LED Light Therapy</strong></p>
                    <p>It’s always recommended that the skin must be cleansed and clean without any make up
                        before LED light therapy treatment. For in-clinic treatments you will be required to
                        wear protective eyewear to protect your eyes from the light.</p>
                </div>
