                <div class="home_vs_clinic pt-30 pt-md-60">
                    <p class="fs-24"><strong>At-Home vs. In Clinic</strong></p>
                    <p>Research and clinical studies have proven that LED light therapy treatments can
                        effectively treat a multitude of skin concerns and provide transformative results.
                        But the results are cumulative, meaning you won’t see long-term benefits from that
                        single salon trip you treat yourself to every so often.</p>
                    <p>In order to see long-term results then regular appointments are required, and these
                        regular in-clinic trips are not only time consuming, but can be very expensive. If
                        regular appointments aren’t an option, investing in a good quality at-home LED light
                        therapy device could be the answer.</p>
                    <p>Though in-clinic LED panels are more powerful than at-home devices, it doesn't mean
                        an at-home device won't be effective or offer the same benefits.</p>
                    <p>At-home LED devices are an excellent way to bring expensive in-clinic treatment to
                        the comfort of your home for a fraction of the price. Remember, LED treatments
                        deliver cumulative results, commitment is key. So this is why particularly at-home
                        LED devices are worth your investment. They allow you to perform regular LED light
                        therapy treatments on your skin at home, which means you’ll be able to see short
                        term results and get long term benefits.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="wear_led_mask pt-30 pt-md-60">
                    <img src="sections/isolated/blogs/images/wear_led_mask.webp" alt=""
                        class="img-fluid d-none d-md-block">
                    <img src="sections/isolated/blogs/images/wear_led_mask_mob.webp" alt=""
                        class="img-fluid d-md-none">
